1.  **Select Provider:** Choose between Fal.ai and Replicate (Fal.ai recommended for speed).
2.  **Prototype:** Build a simple UI to test Wan 2.1 and Kling prompts specifically for financial contexts (e.g., "A line chart showing stock growth", "A professional financial advisor smiling").
3.  **Integration:** Integrate into the PL Capital social media tool.
